To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Thrusting _thrusting;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_thrusting = Thrusting(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_thrusting.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "thrusting", _thrusting.Current.Value);
}
